1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:48,039
Someone saw it firsthand.

3
00:00:48,039 --> 00:00:50,039
Lady Cheng'en killed your son.

4
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:53,079
But she's Her Highness's cousin,

5
00:00:53,079 --> 00:00:55,039
a Lady personally
appointed by His Majesty.

6
00:00:56,039 --> 00:00:57,880
When you come to court,

7
00:00:58,119 --> 00:00:59,920
get ready to die for justice.

8
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,759
Only that can put her on death row.

9
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:04,799
Otherwise, she'll walk free.

10
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,680
In Jinxiu City,

11
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:09,159
only my son can be the bully.

12
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:11,680
She dared to take his life?

13
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:13,519
I'll fight her to the end.

14
00:01:13,540 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 11=

15
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:20,840
Please, seek justice for my son!

16
00:01:21,599 --> 00:01:22,640
(Kill Jia Yi. From Lady Cheng'en.)
Present it!

17
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:32,640
Your Highness,

18
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:33,599
Magistrate Yu,

19
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:36,040
I have something to say.

20
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,079
Speak.

21
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,519
I deserve death ten thousand times.

22
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,799
These words aren't mine to speak.

23
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:46,879
But today,
Lady Cheng'en tried to poison me,

24
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:50,120
and now, Jia Yi's death is tied to her.

25
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,599
These are serious matters.

26
00:01:53,079 --> 00:01:56,000
Especially since Lady Cheng'en
came with you, Your Highness.

27
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:58,040
If word of this spreads,

28
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:00,799
it would disgrace you greatly.

29
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,799
So today, I dare

30
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,439
to ask Lady Cheng'en a question.

31
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:09,000
After you arrived in Jinxiu City,

32
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:12,080
Nanny He, who examined you, died.

33
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:15,080
Now, Jia Yi is dead.

34
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,719
And also,

35
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,120
the elderly couple you claimed

36
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:20,560
were impersonating your parents

37
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:22,680
have vanished too.

38
00:02:23,199 --> 00:02:24,560
The ones harmed by all this

39
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,439
are His Majesty's subjects.

40
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,680
It's fine if I suffer a little.

41
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,400
But I beg Lady Cheng'en,

42
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,680
for the sake of your subjects,

43
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,919
cooperate with Magistrate Yu

44
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,840
to prove your innocence.

45
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,759
Master Wu speaks reasonably.

46
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:50,319
Magistrate Yu,

47
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:52,879
Ruoheng is my cousin

48
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:55,080
and Lady Cheng'en.

49
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:57,120
Lord Cheng'en cares for the people

50
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,280
and is fiercely just.

51
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:01,439
I'm sure my cousin shares his devotion.

52
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,000
Today, I entrust her to you.

53
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:06,840
I trust you'll enforce the law

54
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,599
and give everyone justice.

55
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:10,000
Wise decision, Your Highness.

56
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,280
Wise decision, Your Highness.

57
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:16,319
Lady Cheng'en must stay in jail

58
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:18,800
while I investigate this case.

59
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:22,479
I'll give everyone
a satisfactory answer.

60
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:24,120
Your Highness,

61
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:25,240
Your Honor,

62
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:27,400
though my son held no office,

63
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,800
his life still mattered.

64
00:03:30,319 --> 00:03:31,599
Since current evidence

65
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,919
can't clear Lady Cheng'en,

66
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:36,080
I beg you to be just

67
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:38,120
and put her on death row.

68
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,199
Otherwise,

69
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:42,199
I'll dash my head on this court floor.

70
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:42,919
How dare you!

71
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,439
Lady Cheng'en is of noble birth.

72
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:46,199
She can't just be thrown on death row.

73
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,199
What then?

74
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:50,159
Are you saying Her Highness
is bending the law?

75
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:56,319
Your Highness, you can't let Mr. Jia

76
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:58,319
die right in front of you!

77
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,199
You really are my dear cousin.

78
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:17,759
You won't let me have peace for a day.

79
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,600
Ruoheng,

80
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,240
you've brought disaster after disaster.

81
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:24,839
Better stay on death row a few days.

82
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:27,040
Let Magistrate Yu clear your name.

83
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:29,160
I'll go to jail with Lady Cheng'en.

84
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,040
Wise decision, Your Highness.

85
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,360
My Lady,

86
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,240
this way.

87
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:08,680
Do you think she'll get out alive?

88
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,360
It's dirty.

89
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:15,160
Throw it away for me.

90
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:40,720
This mirror's getting so cloudy.

91
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:44,040
Yesterday, I saw just two lines.

92
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:47,040
Now, there's another.

93
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:52,279
Ever since the phoenix
was recolored,

94
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:56,319
you look even lovelier
than before.

95
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,040
As for the mirror,

96
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:14,040
have a servant replace it tomorrow.

97
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,959
It's been three years now.

98
00:06:18,439 --> 00:06:20,279
The Prince hasn't even stepped

99
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,639
onto the steps to my bedchamber.

100
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:26,240
Forget it.

101
00:06:26,879 --> 00:06:28,439
People change.

102
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,560
The mirror has nothing to do with it.

103
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:34,279
Even if I change the mirror,

104
00:06:34,879 --> 00:06:36,839
I can't get the Prince's heart back.

105
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,360
Your Highness.

106
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,279
Your Highness,

107
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:51,720
the Prince returns soon,

108
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,800
yet Lady Cheng'en is in jail.

109
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:57,000
How will we explain this?

110
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:58,600
What's to explain?

111
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,759
She's just a woman.

112
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,439
If a murder really happened,

113
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,879
the Prince will blame me.

114
00:07:06,439 --> 00:07:09,160
Since I've handed Ruoheng
to the prefectural office,

115
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:11,399
I won't interfere.

116
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:15,959
That way, I'm clear before the Prince.

117
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:18,879
If Lord Cheng'en asks...

118
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,040
If Ruoheng really killed someone,

119
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:23,920
I'm not the one who must answer to him.

120
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,240
Yu Ming is.

121
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:26,959
If she's innocent,

122
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:29,920
I'll welcome her back
as my dear cousin.

123
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,319
You've thought it through well.

124
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,279
But death row

125
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,439
is full of dirty tricks.

126
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,240
No matter the outcome,

127
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:45,240
her temper could use some taming.

128
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,720
Well said, Your Highness.

129
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:50,759
Lady Cheng'en and Master Wu

130
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,360
are both troublemakers.

131
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,920
Nanny Du,

132
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:59,920
some things are better left unsaid.

133
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:04,360
You may go.

134
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,720
Yes.

135
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:16,120
Sorry for the trouble, Your Highness.

136
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,759
I'll take my leave.

137
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:18,920
Wait.

138
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,600
Your temper is getting worse.

139
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,079
Don't forget your place.

140
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:27,199
You're just an embroiderer.

141
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:33,360
I'll remember.

142
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,600
You may go.

143
00:08:45,740 --> 00:08:46,679
(Bring your people to rescue her.)

144
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:48,519
(Bring your people to rescue her.)
If Wu Lian uses death row to trap Rulan,

145
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:49,879
then strikes inside,

146
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:52,399
we won't have any chance.

147
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:54,120
He's vicious and ruthless.

148
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,799
He's hurt so many,

149
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,799
yet for years,

150
00:08:57,799 --> 00:08:59,360
no one could touch him.

151
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,559
Rulan is a Lady now

152
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:02,960
and still locked up.

153
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,840
If something happens to her,

154
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:07,000
Jinxiu City is doomed.

155
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:12,559
Three years ago,
she jumped from the wall.

156
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,399
I knew she was innocent,

157
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,399
but I didn't save her.

158
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,399
Now, she's on death row.

159
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:21,559
I can't watch her die again.

160
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:22,879
Just tell us,

161
00:09:23,639 --> 00:09:24,720
what do we do

162
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,480
to make Magistrate Yu let her go?

163
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,039
Xiaojiu and I have an idea.

164
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,000
Jailbreak.

165
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,679
But death row is tight.

166
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:40,679
Just the two of us are too weak.

167
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,799
Please help us, Mr. Feng.

168
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,759
I know this is dangerous.

169
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:48,120
We may not come back.

170
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,600
But I have no choice.

171
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,840
I entrust my life to you.

172
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:58,240
Please join Xiaojiu and me
in breaking her out.

173
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:00,879
Mr. Liu,

174
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,879
you've always watched out for us.

175
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,440
Your business is the Yehu Gang's.

176
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,399
For Jinxiu City,

177
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:10,320
we'll save Miss Rulan.

178
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,759
We see your righteousness.

179
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:16,000
I'm in for sure.

180
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:20,000
I thank you both for your honor.

181
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:20,879
Cheers.

182
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,360
Cheers.

183
00:10:21,399 --> 00:10:21,720
Cheers.

184
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,159
Master,

185
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:31,840
your hand.

186
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,440
No one can hurt my hand.

187
00:10:36,519 --> 00:10:37,320
Do you believe that?

188
00:10:39,559 --> 00:10:40,279
Wan,

189
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:42,639
keep me company tonight.

190
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:46,360
Tomorrow, send your dear friend
to death.

191
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:19,720
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

192
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:22,960
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

193
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:26,920
♪The past no longer binds♪

194
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:31,120
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

195
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:35,680
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

196
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:39,400
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

197
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,760
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

198
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:45,840
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

199
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,440
♪For your faith that never broke♪

200
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:52,760
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

201
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,560
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

202
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:59,800
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

203
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,480
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

204
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:06,240
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

205
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,840
♪One thought turns into ash♪

206
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:15,160
♪No future left to write♪

207
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:18,040
♪If I never fall♪

208
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,440
♪How could this waiting end♪

209
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:21,800
♪If I bear no scars♪

210
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:24,120
♪How could I challenge fate♪

211
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:26,480
♪I knew there was no way back♪

212
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:30,480
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

213
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,720
♪For your faith that never broke♪

214
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:36,880
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

215
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,760
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

216
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:44,160
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

217
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:47,840
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

218
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:50,440
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

219
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,800
♪One thought turns into ash♪

220
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:59,160
♪No future left to write♪

221
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:02,440
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

222
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,840
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

223
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:09,720
♪If we meet again someday♪

224
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:15,960
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
